+-----------------------------------+
|      Open_Deep_Research_Agent     |
|         System Architecture       |
+-----------------------------------+

[1. User Input]                  [5. Output Generation]
   +------------+                     +------------+
   |  You Ask   |                     | Final Answer|
   | a Question |                     | (Report w/  |
   | (e.g., Chat|                     |  Sources)  |
   +------------+                     +------------+
           |                                   ^
           |                                   |
           v                                   |
[2. Agent Brain]    [3. Tools & Data]          |
   +------------+     +------------+           |
   | AI Thinker |<--->| Helpers:   |           |
   | (Plans &   |     | - Web Search|           |
   |  Decides)  |     | - Databases |           |
   +------------+     | - APIs      |           |
           |          +------------+           |
           |                                   |
           v                                   |
[4. Processing]                                |
   +------------+                              |
   | Analyze &  |------------------------------+
   | Synthesize |
   +------------+

[Feedback Loop: If more info needed, go back to Brain/Tools]

Key:
- Boxes = Main Parts (like robot body parts)
- Arrows = How info flows (like passing a ball)
- <---> = Back-and-forth (like talking to a friend)
